    <briefdescription>
<para><bold> Class <computeroutput>gauss</computeroutput> represent the gaussian density of states </bold> </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Purpose</title><para></para>
</simplesect>
<blockquote><para>This class contains the data structures for representing the density of states for a gaussian with mean <computeroutput>mu_=0</computeroutput> and a standard deviation of <computeroutput>sigma_=1</computeroutput>. </para>
</blockquote></para>
